Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api

Class HttpGetObjectsFromResponseBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api.HttpGetObjectsFromResponseBody
  • public final class HttpGetObjectsFromResponseBody
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to build functions that get data from http body response. These functions return iterables/arrays. Built functions sends requests till desired response is received or waiting time is expired.
